longBusinessSummary: GiG Software p.l.c. provides online gaming services, primarily casino and sports, and a remote gaming platform in Europe, North America, South America, and internationally. The company's flagship solutions include CoreX, an iGaming platform; DataX, a real-time data platform; LogicX, a real-time rules engine; SweepX, a social sweepstakes casino product that offers a dual-wallet system, prize-redemption management, and AI-assisted content management technology; and SportX sportsbook, a sports betting omnichannel solution. It also provides front-end development and managed services, including customer operations, customer relationship management/marketing, and player safety. GiG Software p.l.c. was incorporated in 2024 and is headquartered in St. Julian's, Malta.
